Name: Ittle Dew
About the game: Adventuress Ittle Dew and her sidekick Tippsie crash onto a strange island, filled with loot and mysterious inhabitants. It quickly dawns on the duo that this might become their biggest adventure yet. Ittle Dew boils down the classic adventure formula until there is only fun left. Experience devious puzzles, timeless gameplay and lots of exploration! Lots of secrets and shortcuts to explore Combine your tools in ingenious ways Beautiful hand-drawn HD wobble graphics Speedrunners welcome, with Leaderboards for all the ways you can break the game
